      • parseConversion

        static double parseConversion(java.lang.String convert,
                              double DS,
                              double DT)
        Updates conversion string into a value.

        Conversion string is in the form of D^N where D is either DS or DT and N is an integer exponent. The ^N is not required if N = 1.

        Parameters:
        convert - the conversion string
        DS - the spatial conversion factor
        DT - the temporal conversion factor
        Returns:
        the updated conversion factor
